==English==
===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/naɪ/}}
===Adjective===
'''nigh'''

# [[near]], close by ''(archaic and poetic)''

===Usage Note===
'''Nigh''' is an older form of '''[[near]]'''.  '''Near''' was originally the {{compar}} form of '''nigh'''; the {{superl}} form was '''[[next]]'''.  '''Nigh''' is used today mostly in archaic, poetic, or regional contexts.

